{"tid":1598760,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"突然醒起有樣重要嘢無做過","createTime":"2019-09-27T15:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T16:39:16.000Z","uid":74586,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e79c34c28c41385cb6540490b1a417014721f13","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"拖到去呢一刻，我覺得就算五大訴求都實現晒，都解決唔到件事What&rsquo;s done is done，只有實現港人治港，完全自治先有用，即喺獨立<br />\n<br />\n點解其他人會怕，因為人人都怕陌生同唔熟悉嘅嘢，我哋文宣組要開始講解脫離中共有咩好處，例如現有嘅好處繼續會有，即喺免簽證同關稅地位之類，另外每年慳返買屎水嘅錢可以還富於民，再研發海水化淡之類，基本上已經可以自給自足。<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲咩無肉食之說喺謬誤嚟，要同翻市民講，香港嘅肉只有少部份屬於內地運嚟，但最近豬瘟事件，我諗無人想食佢啲垃圾肉<br />\n<br />\n總括嚟講就喺要人知道無咗中共，香港活得喺更加好，更穩定，更自由"},{"pid":"bfb2f9e31c44e85cb95680827db4ecc2e0f530a4","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"自推一次"},{"pid":"9a01e433446f97a5d09ac7190c8f399a856c1fb4","tid":1598760,"uid":114487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkLvL8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkLvL8O.jpg&h=a79e4b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6yk8mO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6yk8mO.jpg&h=0c2ca0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0dpQz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0dpQz9.jpg&h=1630d9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcJpQz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcJpQz9.jpg&h=d2535f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72f9e4e75d86fe3a659231105fbcf263adbd0209","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T16:04:17.000Z","msg":"推多嘢"},{"pid":"f985ad3131b52185aaa524eb373a0bdd441440d5","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:25:43.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"6763e1f5e64c4b79d637f64af5b5f2635b6f189c","tid":1598760,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:27:30.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得之前話嗌光復香港時代革命都畀人當on9"},{"pid":"d3229068453002ed1c13f39601b788cd483d43a9","tid":1598760,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:28:18.000Z","msg":"心態要調整<br />\n求幫推 或多或少有幫助<br />\n［反省］我發現好多人都搵唔到方向及定位 入嚟啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7dc9ac7e52c61eb3301bcfc116ad803a44db7da3","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6763e1f5e64c4b79d637f64af5b5f2635b6f189c","tid":1598760,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:27:30.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得之前話嗌光復香港時代革命都畀人當on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:28:57.000Z","msg":"我記得第一次嗌喺7月21中環，嗰時喺我第一次搵到自己對呢場運動嘅歸屬"},{"pid":"0f74fd558ebf03e5a91450b02e883bd5879f7957","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"真喺唔好再怕港獨喺禁語，呢一刻唔獨立埋無機會了，唔通28年後先再爭取咩，天時地理人和都齊晒，喺差我哋同多啲人講獨立有咩好處，有啲咩比以往仲要好，所有生活唔變之餘仲會更加好<br />\n<br />\n我哋要畀<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望</span></strong>呢嗰社會，唔喺宣傳自己有幾慘，班狗有幾唔人道<br />\n<br />\n我哋為一真喺可以拉晒班狗就只有獨立！"},{"pid":"ea66fb7f2404deeebca58b5c5b6d6f752dcf627c","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"推唔郁好慘"},{"pid":"34cd780cee5be3fa17ebdebd3f7e58ecff47f693","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:03:02.000Z","msg":"推啊，得我一個推到幾時"},{"pid":"b7798b2c876d18466713ab1328ad920115fdfb2e","tid":1598760,"uid":74586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef22951e8c6d0f042b3d3f1f3bc9ce25c0f856ad","tid":1598760,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09